You are implementing Task 4 and Task 5 together (they are small changes).

## Task 4: Consumer - check isSyncPush on scheduled publish

File: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-server/src/main/java/com/yottastudios/ns/collabspace/announcement/consumer/AnnouncementConsumer.java`

In the `handle()` method, find this line:
```java
         // 同步推送到 Knock + MM
         announcementPushService.pushAnnouncement(announce);
```

Replace it with:
```java
         // 同步推送到 Knock + MM（根据开关）
         if (Boolean.TRUE.equals(announce.getIsSyncPush())) {
             announcementPushService.pushAnnouncement(announce);
             log.info("[lbl][2421-同步推送][Announcement][SCHEDULED] 定时发布推送, id={}", announcementId);
         } else {
             log.info("[lbl][2421-同步推送][Announcement][SCHEDULED] 同步推送关闭，跳过推送, id={}", announcementId);
         }
```

## Task 5: Restore pushToMm in AnnouncementPushService

File: `D:/project/pt-gitlab/collabspace/collabspace-server/src/main/java/com/yottastudios/ns/collabspace/announcement/service/impl/AnnouncementPushService.java`

In the `pushAnnouncement()` method, find:
```java
        pushToKnock(announcement);
//        pushToMm(announcement);
```

Replace with:
```java
        pushToKnock(announcement);
        pushToMm(announcement);
```

